          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "Dinner time - I’m starving. We sit inside while Filen plays guitar and I talk quietly with a woman called (Carin) Krog who is an adventure mom of note. She tells me stories of their family motorcycle trips around Africa, the Camino trail and other adventures. She drove around Malawi on an XT500… who is this legend. She lives in Howick; classic.",
            "link": null
